#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:10004
#: d011d258685b42c5b013e6cd7a69721d
msgid ""
"Causal identification is about figuring out if we can prove a cause-and-"
"effect relationship using the data we have and our assumptions. This "
"process helps us establish clear links between different factors instead "
"of looking at their correlations. It is essential when working with "
"observational data, which can be affected by hidden factors and biases "
"that make it hard to see true causal relationships."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:10006
#: f1869d70c0e74885a15a32e3a9b13d90
msgid ""
