#: 56d194f3aea041fca23ccbe81ef23084
msgid ""
"In this section, we simulate two marketing channels, $x1$ and $x2$, which"
" represent different advertising channels (e.g., Search ads and Social "
"media campaigns). Each channel's behavior is influenced by random "
"variability and confounding effects from seasonal holidays and competitor"
" actions. Hereâ€™s how we model each channel mathematically:"
