#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:160015
#: 7ff75f20b66a430abc982eb29a8b4387
msgid ""
"**Channel $x2$**: On the other hand, we generate $x2$ which is affected "
"by the holiday signal, the influence of $x1$ and the competitor offers. "
"We could define it as:"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:160018
#: 3cbedfc36be345ff9c66daef47d24ed8
